Sad Doge

A commonly known fact about Shiba Inus is their squishy faces and fluffy neckrolls, and Doge is no different IRL. This photo of the Shiba “Kabosu” was taken by her owner Atsuko Sato in February 2010, subsequently kicking off the Doge meme in the years to come. Since then, Kabosu has become the most well-known Shibe on the entire internet.
